title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jun 9 2022

description:
Millions of Americans will never know a leftist tried to kill Justice Kavanaugh because the media isn't covering it. Clay says, "To me, this is one of the biggest stories in judicial history and it's being buried." The Biden regime wanted high gas prices and got it done. Biden slips and falls again boarding Are Force One, wears mask backstage on Kimmel and then rips it off for a long, close interview. New Yorker Buck says Eric Adams doesn't know what he's talking about or he's lying when he says crime is caused by the right giving people guns, and that "he's just not up for the job, folks." Only 30% of Americans think Biden is doing a good job.
